![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ab1c9b00-8413-410b-b445-2b8a5485e94a/13774.jpg)

Becky Lynch opens Smackdown in Dublin, Ireland. The crowd has a massive eruption for her but Becky turns on them immediately by telling them they don't deserve this show.

The crowd chants for Lyra Valkyria. Then they start chanting for CM Punk and Becky says “Nobody wants that old ass!”

Tiffany Stratton comes out to question why Becky Lynch is on her show. Which brings out Nia Jax.

The heels attack Tiffany Stratton but she's saved by Jade Cargill.

Becky Lynch & Nia Jax vs. Tiffany Stratton & Jade Cargill is announced for the main event tonight.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5c57c872-a73b-4ca9-8924-7f58300c943b/13775.jpg)

