![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e2816e97-3474-4754-8079-c516e7680171/13776.jpg)

*   ## **_MELO DON'T MIZ DEF. MCMG_**
    

Ireland LOVES the Miz 💀💀

We Want Miz, Miz is Awesome. Massive pops anytime he was in the ring. The Miz tries to tag himself in the way he did last week but Melo protests. Alex Shelly shoves Melo into the Miz and they almost lose the match but Miz does tag himself in and gets the win.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8bff8143-c413-473d-aa56-420bc3c58979/processed_13779.jpg)

