![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/146d5b92-ebe4-4025-96a0-2f832582f2ac/13780.jpg)

Backstage segment with Solo Sikoa coming up to Jimmy Uso to congratulate him on the baby.

He wants Jimmy to name the baby after Uncle Solo 💀

Sami Zayn says stop worrying about naming other people's babies and start worrying about keeping that US Title because WRESTLEMANIA MAIN EVENTER Sami Zayn is coming for it at Clash in Paris.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7f62bbf7-c4e3-4c41-a456-83ccbf398f05/13781.jpg)

*   ## **_PIPER NIVEN_** **_DEF. CHARLOTTE FLAIR_**
    

Joe Tessatore announced that Alexa Bliss is not able to be here tonight due to the beatdown last week from Chelsea Green and the Secret HERvice

This allows Chelsea Green to run interference undisturbed and cost Charlotte this match against Piper Niven

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1ab13699-5e99-4e55-ae3b-d6b5ca8eb8eb/13782.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fa13e2fe-3ee9-49ba-a761-145bc69202a4/13785.jpg)

Michin wants a US Title match from Giulia but Kiana James says Michin will have to go through her first.

Michin vs Kiana James is set.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c4b56747-3390-42d6-9708-ea063d80f2e7/13790.jpg)

**_“IT'S A DISAPPOINTMENT BECAUSE WE WERE SO EXCITED THAT YOU CAME TO WWE, WE OPENED OUR ARMS BUT INSTEAD OF APPRECIATING ALL THIS, WHAT DID YOU DO?"_**

**_"YOU USE US AS A MARKETING STRATEGY TO BUY ANOTHER POKEMON CARD”_**

Logan Paul says John Cena is an outsider now and Logan Paul is the wrestler. Logan says he doesn't need to get naked at the Oscars to get attention. This is Logan Paul's house now.

John Cena drops a pipe bomb on Logan. He says Logan Paul is right, he is not an outsider. He's a disappointment.

WWE opens their arms for him and he uses them as a franchise opportunity. Logan Paul is facing John Cena and wasting a spot that could go to people like Dom Mysterio or AJ Styles.

Logan has said he puts his life on the line when he gets in the ring. Logan Paul has had 23 matches in his entire time in the WWE. John Cena has been here 23 years.

At Clash in Paris, Logan Paul is going to step into the ring with the greatest of all time. Logan slaps the hat off of Cena's head and gets an FU for his troubles.

Cena stands tall to end the segment.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a613b523-3cd4-48a9-b8b7-a76ed8f13269/13794.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b9197259-b540-4576-ad14-43381e06efb7/13795.jpg)

Drew McIntyre finds Logan Paul backstage and gives him advice. Drew says Logan is scared of the mystique of "Super Cena". He tells Logan he still has an opportunity to make it right tonight, by any means necessary.

He looks Logan in the eye and reiterates... By any. Means. Necessary.

